
<div class="centered_feed round_rec">

  <div class="dives_index_wrapper clear-fix">

    <h1 class="inside_titles divelog_title">Edit divesite</h1>

    <form action="/divesites/<%=@divesite.slug%>" method="post">
      <input type="hidden" name="_method" value="patch">
      <div class="row">
        <input class="triple_column_inputs" type="text" name="divesite[name]" placeholder="Divesite name" value="<%=@divesite.name.titleize%>">
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <input class="triple_column_inputs not_first" type="text" name="divesite[location]" placeholder="Location" value="<%=@divesite.location.titleize%>">
        <input class="triple_column_inputs not_first" type="text" name="divesite[country]" placeholder="Country" value="<%=@divesite.country.titleize%>">
      </div>
  <br></br>
    <br></br>

<div class="row">
<pre>
<p>Are you also logging a new dive at this divesite?
If so, here's the place to do it!</p></pre>
</div>
<div class="row">
  <input class="triple_column_inputs" type="text" id="date" name="dive[date]" placeholder="Dive date DD/MM/YYYY">
  <input class="triple_column_inputs not_first" type="text" name="dive[time]" placeholder="Start time">
  <input class="triple_column_inputs not_first" type="integer" name="dive[length]" placeholder="Length(mins)">
</div>
<div class="row">
  <textarea rows="5" class="triple_column_inputs" name="dive[notes]" placeholder="Your dive notes"></textarea>
</div>
<br></br>
  <br></br>
    <br></br>


        <div class="row">
        <pre>
        <p>All dives logged at this divesite will be updated.
          Are you sure you want to go ahead?</p></pre>
        </div>
      <div class="row">
        <input class="single_column_links" type="submit" value="Update Divesite">
      </div>

      <br></br>
    </form>


  </div>
</div>
